  "names": [
    {
      "full_name": "State Unitary Enterprise of the \"Republic of Crimea\" \"Chernomorneftegaz\"",
      "is_primary": true
    }
  ],
  "remarks": "On 17 Mar 2014, the \"Parliament of Crimea\" adopted a resolution declaring the appropriation of assets belonging to Chernomorneftegaz enterprise on behalf of the \"Republic of Crimea\". The enterprise is thus effectively confiscated by the Crimean \"authorities\". Re-registered on 29 Nov 2014 as State Unitary Enterprise of the \"Republic of Crimea\" \"Chernomorneftegaz\" (Государственное унитарное предприятие Республики Крым \"Черноморнефтегаз\"). Founder: The Ministry of Fuel and Energy of the \"Republic of Crimea\" (Министерство топлива и энергетики \"Республики Крым\").",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}